ks/3815780282fa1bc8.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/54f16660fae19f85.js\" async=\"\"></script><meta name=\"next-size-adjust\" content=\"\"/><title>Training &amp; Development | Humam Consulting</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Specialized culinary and operational training programs for the food industry.\"/><meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"Humam Consulting,Food Safety,Quality Assurance,Facility Design,Corporate Training,ISO Certifications,Saudi Arabia Consulting\"/><meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Humam Consulting | Expert Quality Assurance\"/><meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Premium expertise in food safety, quality assurance, facility design, and specialized training.\"/><meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://humamconsulting.com\"/><meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"Humam Consulting\"/><meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"Humam Consulting\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"Expert consultancy and quality assurance for the food industry.\"/><link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"/images/brand/Humam-Logo-Short.svg\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico?favicon.0b3bf435.ico\" sizes=\"256x256\" type=\"image/x-icon\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/images/brand/Humam-Logo-Short.svg\"/><link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" href=\"/images/brand/Humam-Logo-Short.svg\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/a6dad97d9634a72d.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><nav class=\"Navbar-module__O8Na-a__navbar \"><div class=\"container Navbar-module__O8Na-a__inner\"><a href=\"/ar\"><img alt=\"Logo\" width=\"100\" height=\"70\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fbrand%2F&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fbrand%2F&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fbrand%2F&amp;w=256&amp;q=75\"/></a><ul class=\"Navbar-module__O8Na-a__navLinks\"><li><a href=\"/ar\">الرئيسية</a></li><li><a href=\"/ar/about\">من نحن</a></li><li><a href=\"/ar/services\">خدماتنا</a></li><li><a href=\"/ar/training-center\">مركز التدريب</a></li><li><a href=\"/ar/contact\">تواصل معنا</a></li></ul><div class=\"Navbar-module__O8Na-a__actions\"><button class=\"LanguageSwitcher-module__OkSVoa__button\" aria-label=\"Toggle language\"><span class=\"LanguageSwitcher-module__OkSVoa__icon\">🇺🇸</span><span class=\"LanguageSwitcher-module__OkSVoa__text\">English</span></button></div><button class=\"Navbar-module__O8Na-a__hamburger\" aria-label=\"Open menu\" aria-expanded=\"false\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></button></div><div class=\"Navbar-module__O8Na-a__mobileMenu \"><div class=\"Navbar-module__O8Na-a__mobileMenuHeader\"><button class=\"Navbar-module__O8Na-a__closeButton\" aria-label=\"Close menu\"><span></span><span></span></button></div><ul class=\"Navbar-module__O8Na-a__mobileNavLinks\"><li><a href=\"/ar\">الرئيسية</a></li><li><a href=\"/ar/about\">من نحن</a></li><li><a href=\"/ar/services\">خدماتنا</a></li><li><a href=\"/ar/training-center\">مركز التدريب</a></li><li><a href=\"/ar/contact\">تواصل معنا</a></li></ul><div class=\"Navbar-module__O8Na-a__mobileActions\"><button class=\"LanguageSwitcher-module__OkSVoa__button\" aria-label=\"Toggle language\"><span class=\"LanguageSwitcher-module__OkSVoa__icon\">🇺🇸</span><span class=\"LanguageSwitcher-module__OkSVoa__text\">English</span></button></div></div></nav><main><section class=\"ServicesHero-module__qYtEbG__hero\"><div class=\"ServicesHero-module__qYtEbG__heroWrapper\"><div class=\"ServicesHero-module__qYtEbG__background\"><div class=\"ServicesHero-module__qYtEbG__brandWatermark\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.8) rotate(-15deg)\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M50 0C50 27.6142 72.3858 50 100 50C72.3858 50 50 72.3858 50 100C50 72.3858 27.6142 50 0 50C27.6142 50 50 27.6142 50 0Z\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-green)\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"ServicesHero-module__qYtEbG__brandWatermarkSecondary\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.9)\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M50 0 C22.3858 0 0 22.3858 0 50 C0 77.6142 22.3858 100 50 100\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-cream)\"></path><path d=\"M50 0 C77.6142 0 100 22.3858 100 50 C100 77.6142 77.6142 100 50 100\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-red)\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"ServicesHero-module__qYtEbG__overlay\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-brand-dark-olive) 0%, #e6b85c 100%)\"></div></div><div class=\"ServicesHero-module__qYtEbG__content\"><div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;opacity:0\"><div class=\"ServicesHero-module__qYtEbG__badge\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">حوّل الفرق. ارتقِ بالأداء.</div><h1 class=\"ServicesHero-module__qYtEbG__title\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">التدريب والتطوير</h1><p class=\"ServicesHero-module__qYtEbG__subtitle\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">برامج متخصصة تبني القدرات وتغرس التميز وتحقق تأثيراً تشغيلياً دائماً على كل مستوى في مؤسستك.</p></div></div></div></section><div class=\"PatternDivider-module__ZW-8xG__divider \" style=\"background-image:url(/patterns/pattern-zigzag-strip.png)\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><section class=\"section TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__wrapper\"><div class=\"container TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__gridContainer\"><div class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__header\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><span class=\"eyebrow\">فلسفة التدريب</span><h2 class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__heading\">معرفة تنتقل. مهارات تبقى.</h2><p class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__description\">برامجنا التدريبية مصممة من قبل ممارسين وليس منظّرين. كل جلسة تجمع بين التطبيق العملي والتجربة الواقعية — لأن التغيير الدائم يحدث بالممارسة لا بالتعلم فقط.</p></div><div class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__grid\" style=\"opacity:0\"><div class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__backgroundPattern\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 120 360\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\"><rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-green)\"></rect><path d=\"M30 5C30 19 41 30 55 30C41 30 30 41 30 55C30 41 19 30 5 30C19 30 30 19 30 5Z\" fill=\"white\"></path><rect x=\"60\" y=\"0\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-red)\"></rect><ellipse cx=\"90\" cy=\"10\" rx=\"12\" ry=\"20\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-mustard)\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"90\" cy=\"50\" rx=\"12\" ry=\"20\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-mustard)\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"70\" cy=\"30\" rx=\"20\" ry=\"12\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-mustard)\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"110\" cy=\"30\" rx=\"20\" ry=\"12\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-mustard)\"></ellipse><rect x=\"0\" y=\"60\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-red)\"></rect><ellipse cx=\"30\" cy=\"70\" rx=\"12\" ry=\"20\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-mustard)\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"30\" cy=\"110\" rx=\"12\" ry=\"20\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-mustard)\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"10\" cy=\"90\" rx=\"20\" ry=\"12\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-mustard)\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"50\" cy=\"90\" rx=\"20\" ry=\"12\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-mustard)\"></ellipse><rect x=\"60\" y=\"60\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-green)\"></rect><path d=\"M90 65C90 79 101 90 115 90C101 90 90 101 90 115C90 101 79 90 65 90C79 90 90 79 90 65Z\" fill=\"white\"></path><rect x=\"0\" y=\"120\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-green)\"></rect><path d=\"M30 125C30 139 41 150 55 150C41 150 30 161 30 175C30 161 19 150 5 150C19 150 30 139 30 125Z\" fill=\"white\"></path><rect x=\"60\" y=\"120\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-red)\"></rect><ellipse cx=\"90\" cy=\"130\" rx=\"12\" ry=\"20\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-mustard)\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"90\" cy=\"170\" rx=\"12\" ry=\"20\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-mustard)\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"70\" cy=\"150\" rx=\"20\" ry=\"12\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-mustard)\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"110\" cy=\"150\" rx=\"20\" ry=\"12\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-mustard)\"></ellipse><rect x=\"0\" y=\"180\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-red)\"></rect><ellipse cx=\"30\" cy=\"190\" rx=\"12\" ry=\"20\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-mustard)\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"30\" cy=\"230\" rx=\"12\" ry=\"20\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-mustard)\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"10\" cy=\"210\" rx=\"20\" ry=\"12\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-mustard)\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"50\" cy=\"210\" rx=\"20\" ry=\"12\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-mustard)\"></ellipse><rect x=\"60\" y=\"180\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-green)\"></rect><path d=\"M90 185C90 199 101 210 115 210C101 210 90 221 90 235C90 221 79 210 65 210C79 210 90 199 90 185Z\" fill=\"white\"></path><rect x=\"0\" y=\"240\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-green)\"></rect><path d=\"M30 245C30 259 41 270 55 270C41 270 30 281 30 295C30 281 19 270 5 270C19 270 30 259 30 245Z\" fill=\"white\"></path><rect x=\"60\" y=\"240\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-red)\"></rect><ellipse cx=\"90\" cy=\"250\" rx=\"12\" ry=\"20\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-mustard)\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"90\" cy=\"290\" rx=\"12\" ry=\"20\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-mustard)\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"70\" cy=\"270\" rx=\"20\" ry=\"12\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-mustard)\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"110\" cy=\"270\" rx=\"20\" ry=\"12\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-mustard)\"></ellipse><rect x=\"0\" y=\"300\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-red)\"></rect><ellipse cx=\"30\" cy=\"310\" rx=\"12\" ry=\"20\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-mustard)\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"30\" cy=\"350\" rx=\"12\" ry=\"20\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-mustard)\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"10\" cy=\"330\" rx=\"20\" ry=\"12\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-mustard)\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"50\" cy=\"330\" rx=\"20\" ry=\"12\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-mustard)\"></ellipse><rect x=\"60\" y=\"300\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-green)\"></rect><path d=\"M90 305C90 319 101 330 115 330C101 330 90 341 90 355C90 341 79 330 65 330C79 330 90 319 90 305Z\" fill=\"white\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__programCard\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__cardWatermark\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M50 0C50 27.6142 72.3858 50 100 50C72.3858 50 50 72.3858 50 100C50 72.3858 27.6142 50 0 50C27.6142 50 50 27.6142 50 0Z\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-mustard)\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__cardNumber\">01</div><h3 class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__cardTitle\">تدريب الموظفين</h3><p class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__cardDesc\">برامج تأسيسية شاملة لفرق المطبخ والخدمة ومديري العمليات. نبني الكفاءة الأساسية التي تتطلبها العمليات المتميزة.</p><div class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__outcomesSection\"><span class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__outcomesLabel\">Outcomes</span><div class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__outcomesGrid\"><div class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__outcomeItem\"><div class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__outcomeDot\"></div><span>تحسين التعامل مع الغذاء، توحيد الإجراءات، تقليل الهدر، رفع ثقة الفريق</span></div></div></div></div><div class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__programCard\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__cardWatermark\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M50 0C50 27.6142 72.3858 50 100 50C72.3858 50 50 72.3858 50 100C50 72.3858 27.6142 50 0 50C27.6142 50 50 27.6142 50 0Z\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-mustard)\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__cardNumber\">02</div><h3 class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__cardTitle\">تطوير الطهاة</h3><p class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__cardDesc\">برامج طهي متقدمة تركز على صقل التقنيات وابتكار القوائم والقيادة المطبخية والتطوير الإبداعي للطهاة المحترفين.</p><div class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__outcomesSection\"><span class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__outcomesLabel\">Outcomes</span><div class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__outcomesGrid\"><div class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__outcomeItem\"><div class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__outcomeDot\"></div><span>تقنيات محسنة، قدرة على ابتكار القوائم، مهارات قيادية، ثقة إبداعية</span></div></div></div></div><div class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__programCard\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__cardWatermark\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M50 0C50 27.6142 72.3858 50 100 50C72.3858 50 50 72.3858 50 100C50 72.3858 27.6142 50 0 50C27.6142 50 50 27.6142 50 0Z\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-mustard)\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__cardNumber\">03</div><h3 class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__cardTitle\">ورش العمل</h3><p class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__cardDesc\">ورش عمل مكثفة ومركزة على مواضيع محددة — من الامتثال لسلامة الغذاء إلى ممارسات الاستدامة وتحليل اتجاهات القطاع.</p><div class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__outcomesSection\"><span class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__outcomesLabel\">Outcomes</span><div class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__outcomesGrid\"><div class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__outcomeItem\"><div class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__outcomeDot\"></div><span>اكتساب مهارات مستهدف، جاهزية للشهادات، خطط تنفيذ عملية</span></div></div></div></div><div class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__programCard\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__cardWatermark\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M50 0C50 27.6142 72.3858 50 100 50C72.3858 50 50 72.3858 50 100C50 72.3858 27.6142 50 0 50C27.6142 50 50 27.6142 50 0Z\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-mustard)\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__cardNumber\">04</div><h3 class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__cardTitle\">البرامج المتخصصة</h3><p class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__cardDesc\">برامج تدريبية مصممة خصيصاً لتحدياتك التشغيلية المحددة وتركيبة فريقك وأهداف عملك.</p><div class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__outcomesSection\"><span class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__outcomesLabel\">Outcomes</span><div class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__outcomesGrid\"><div class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__outcomeItem\"><div class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__outcomeDot\"></div><span>تطوير مهارات مخصص، مواءمة تشغيلية، تحسين أداء قابل للقياس</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__ctaSection\"><div class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__ctaBg\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__ctaWatermark\"><path d=\"M50 0 C22.3858 0 0 22.3858 0 50 C0 77.6142 22.3858 100 50 100\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-cream)\"></path><path d=\"M50 0 C77.6142 0 100 22.3858 100 50 C100 77.6142 77.6142 100 50 100\" fill=\"var(--color-brand-red)\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"container TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__ctaContent\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><span class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__ctaEyebrow\">مستعد للاستثمار في فريقك؟</span><h2 class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__ctaTitle\">اطلب برنامجاً تدريبياً</h2><p class=\"TrainingPrograms-module__gzjRqG__ctaDesc\">أخبرنا عن فريقك وأهدافك. سنصمم برنامجاً يحقق نتائج قابلة للقياس.</p><a class=\"Button-module__VMVMAW__linkWrapper\" href=\"/ar/contact\"><div class=\"Button-module__VMVMAW__btn Button-module__VMVMAW__outline\" tabindex=\"0\">اطلب تدريباً</div></a></div></div></section></main><!--$--><!--/$--><footer class=\"Footer-module__yg9ahW__footer\"><div class=\"container Footer-module__yg9ahW__inner\"><div class=\"Footer-module__yg9ahW__leftColumn\"><div class=\"Footer-module__yg9ahW__brand\"><a href=\"/ar\"><img alt=\"Logo\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" style=\"color:transparent\" src=\"/images/brand/Humam-Logo.svg\"/></a><p>Expert consultancy, structural planning, and quality assurance for the modern catering and food industry.</p></div><div class=\"Footer-module__yg9ahW__contactInfo\"><p>Makkah, Saudi Arabia</p><p class=\"Footer-module__yg9ahW__email\">info@humam.sa</p></div></div><div class=\"Footer-module__yg9ahW__rightColumn\"><div class=\"Footer-module__yg9ahW__linkGroup\"><h4>Company</h4><ul><li><a href=\"/ar/about\">About Us</a></li><li><a href=\"/ar/services\">Services</a></li><li><a href=\"/ar/industries\">Industries</a></li><li><a href=\"/ar/experts\">Our Experts</a></li><li><a href=\"/ar/contact\">Contact</a></li></ul></div><div class=\"Footer-module__yg9ahW__linkGroup\"><h4>Expertise</h4><ul><li><a href=\"/ar/services#development\">Business Development</a></li><li><a href=\"/ar/services#quality\">Quality &amp; Safety</a></li><li><a href=\"/ar/services#training\">Training</a></li><li><a href=\"/ar/services#planning\">Structural Planning</a></li></ul></div><div class=\"Footer-module__yg9ahW__linkGroup\"><h4>Legal</h4><ul><li><a href=\"/ar/privacy\">Privacy Policy</a></li><li><a href=\"/ar/terms\">Terms of Service</a></li><li><a href=\"/ar/cookies\">Cookie Policy</a></li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"Footer-module__yg9ahW__bottomBar\"><div class=\"Footer-module__yg9ahW__bottomLinks\"><p>© <!-- -->20